The paper discusses a logical notation for describing properties of relational structures in shape analysis, databases, and knowledge bases. This falls under the scope of several sub-categories, including logic (cs.LO), databases (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), programming languages (cs.PL), and software engineering (cs.SE). However, since the paper focuses on logical notation and its application to shape analysis and databases, cs.LO and cs.DB are the most likely sub-categories.
